description: The calendar date this summary would be displayed on in Garmin Connect. The date format is ‘yyyy-mm-dd’.
Start time of the summary in seconds since January 1, 1970, 00:00:00 UTC (Unix timestamp).
Offset in seconds to add to startTimeInSeconds to derive the "local" time of the device that captured the data.
The duration of the measurement period in seconds.
Collection of key-value pairs where the key is offset in seconds from the startTimeInSeconds and the value is the SpO2 measurement taken at that time (1 sample/minute)
